        "pitch_and_presentation": 6
    },

    "final_verdict": "Echoverse shows promising potential with its AI-driven interactive storytelling approach, earning a combined score of 6/10. For further development, priority should be given to: 1) Expanding device compatibility, 2) Implementing multi-character story support, 3) Adding unique features to differentiate from competitors, and 4) Conducting user testing. While the project demonstrates impressive achievement for a first-time developer, addressing these areas would significantly strengthen its market position. The foundation is solid, but additional development is needed to transform it from a promising prototype into a commercially viable product."
